2001-02-06  Benjamin Kosnik  <bkoz@redhat.com>

	* acinclude.m4 (GLIBCPP_EXPORT_INSTALL_INFO): Deal with library
	install locations too.
	* aclocal.m4: Regenerate.
	* configure.in: Remove USE_LIBDIR.
	* configure: Regenerate.
